            <div class="opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper ">

                    <span class="opener__topics  opener__topics--vertical-rule">
            <a class="opener__topics-link " href="https://www.propublica.org/topics/education">Education</a>
        </span>
    
    <h1 class="opener__hed " >        Skipping School: America’s Hidden Education Crisis
    </h1>

    <h2 class="opener__dek " >        Absenteeism has nearly doubled since the pandemic. With state and federal governments largely abdicating any role in getting kids back into classrooms, some schools have turned to private companies for a reimagined version of the truant officer.
    </h2>

    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
